Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,P,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:09.98,Default,Farnese,0,0,0,,We finally found you, Black Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:14.49,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:16.81,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Is that a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:17.98,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:19.99,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,How could anyone wield that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:22.49,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,This man is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:25.00,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,the Hawk of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.57,0:00:28.95,Default,F,0,0,0,,We are the Holy See's Holy Iron Chain Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:33.01,Default,F,0,0,0,,We have made haste, by order of \Nthe Miracle Certification Bureau,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to take you to the Holy See.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:37.01,Default,F,0,0,0,,You will not be harmed if you lay \Ndown your sword and surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:41.18,Default,F,0,0,0,,If not, we swear upon God \Nthat you will be captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:43.97,Default,G,0,0,0,,I don't recall doing anything that'd \Nmake a priest arrest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:45.61,Default,F,0,0,0,,How callous...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:47.30,Default,F,0,0,0,,What is all that blood from?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:48.50,Default,F,0,0,0,,While tracking you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:52.27,Default,F,0,0,0,,we saw the bodies of a monk, \Nhis daughter, and countless others.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:54.78,Default,P,0,0,0,,Guts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.19,Default,F,0,0,0,,The time for talk is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:00:58.28,Default,F,0,0,0,,This is God's will!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:00.70,Default,F,0,0,0,,Troops, capture the Black Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.97,0:01:08.13,Default,P,0,0,0,,This doesn't look good...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:08.92,Default,P,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:22.14,Title,Ep Title,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,225)}The Holy Iron Chain Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.89,Default - flashback,G,0,0,0,,Listen, I'll create an opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:53.74,Default - flashback,G,0,0,0,,When I do, race through the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:56.06,Default - flashback,Casca,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:57.81,Default - flashback,G,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:03:01.00,Default - flashback,G,0,0,0,,Do you really want to die like this, \Nin the middle of nowhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:04.66,Default - flashback,G,0,0,0,,A good blade should rest in a scabbard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:08.74,Default - flashback,G,0,0,0,,You should return to the master of your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:17.02,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,What's his deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:18.34,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,He can't use his sword at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:19.46,Default,P,0,0,0,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.21,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,I can't get a good grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:22.32,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:23.72,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Have at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:25.80,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Idiot, don't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:26.81,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,H-He's fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.64,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Stop, you'll kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.26,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,His false hand! Watch that hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:37.70,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Calm down! Don't get worked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:39.56,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Surround him! Don't let him move around!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.14,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,We'll just hit each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.09,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:46.00,Default,F,0,0,0,,Idiots! We can't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:56.42,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,The whole lot of you is pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.92,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,How can a single fugitive \Nhave you in such disarray?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:00.85,Default,Serpico,0,0,0,,You can't blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:03.75,Default,Serpico,0,0,0,,The Holy Iron Chain Knights, also known \Nas the "Spoiled Brat Knights,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:06.78,Default,Serpico,0,0,0,,are full of pampered heirs their \Nnoble families wanted safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:09.76,Default,Serpico,0,0,0,,They're here for the prestige \Nand safety the order affords.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:12.95,Default,Serpico,0,0,0,,Most have never fought in a real battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.35,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Thank you for the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:17.17,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,So, why are you here, Sir Serpico?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:18.29,Default,Serpico,0,0,0,,Oh, come now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:19.75,Default,Serpico,0,0,0,,I'm sure you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:22.99,Default,Serpico,0,0,0,,I became an officer of arms because \NI hate the sight of blood—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:32.57,Default,F,0,0,0,,Good... Now! Secure him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:33.80,Default,Serpico,0,0,0,,Oh, crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:56.58,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,This is the Black Swordsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:05:00.00,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,His malice is unmistakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:02.72,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,He is the one written of in Revelations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:04.28,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Lady Farnese...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:06.40,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,As Serpico stated,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:09.47,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,given our troops' combat inexperience, \Nwe face mounting casualties
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:11.66,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,if we seek to overwhelm him with numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:15.29,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,I ask that you allow me, Azan, \Nto undertake this task!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:23.22,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Back, back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:24.42,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Back, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:25.62,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,Vice-commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:26.38,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,Sir Azan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:29.47,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,I am Azan, Second-in-Command of \Nthe Holy Iron Chain Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:33.18,Default,P,0,0,0,,Wow, we'll never run out \Nof surprises around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:34.92,Default,G,0,0,0,,Iron Staff Demon Azan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:36.20,Default,G,0,0,0,,I've heard of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:39.22,Default,G,0,0,0,,I believe you're also called \Nthe Knight of the Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:40.15,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:42.36,Default,P,0,0,0,,You know this guy, Guts?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:47.31,Default,Guts,0,0,0,,The story goes that an injured old man \Nwas standing on a narrow bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:49.76,Default,Guts,0,0,0,,The Knight of the Bridge was a curious guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:52.78,Default,Guts,0,0,0,,who refused to let an army of \Na hundred mounted men pass
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:54.66,Default,Guts,0,0,0,,because he was protecting that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:57.03,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,That was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:06:01.92,Default,G,0,0,0,,People laughed and said he could've ended it \Nby carrying the old man to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:05.90,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,A knight has a duty to uphold \Nhis code of chivalry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.91,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,My circumstances led to being a cleric knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:09.82,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,In any event, I have named myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:12.18,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,If you are a knight, \Ncourtesy demands you reciprocate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.87,Default,G,0,0,0,,I'm no knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:14.85,Default,G,0,0,0,,I'm Guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:16.68,Default,G,0,0,0,,Just "Guts," old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.66,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Very well, Guts...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:19.69,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:21.27,Default,Serpico,0,0,0,,He's so old-fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:24.40,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Prepare to break at least one or two bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:30.86,Default - italics,Guts,0,0,0,,One or two bones, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.62,Default - italics,Guts,0,0,0,,I can't keep dodging with this gimpy leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:41.68,Default - italics,Guts,0,0,0,,And the old man isn't just an idiot \Nwho relies on brute strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:46.00,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,You nimble trickster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:48.21,Default - italics,Azan,0,0,0,,Summer Showers Thrust!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:53.22,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Vice-commander Azan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:57.80,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,I would commend you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:07:02.31,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,But given your lack of offense, \Nyour execution lacks finesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:04.13,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Your swordsmanship\Naffirmed its battle-testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:06.28,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,I'll admit it thrilled me, \Nhearkening to my own past.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:09.63,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,I must apply myself to the order \Nwith greater diligence,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to mend my foolish ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:13.36,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:15.45,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,I can barely feel my limbs anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.56,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:21.90,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,A frontal attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:22.98,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Commendable resolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.08,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:27.75,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,I was careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.43,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Lady Farnese!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:57.49,Default,F,0,0,0,,I was the one who put him down?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:59.65,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Well done, Lady Farnese.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:01.58,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,You really are our Lady Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:03.37,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.93,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Wait, is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:07.08,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,He's unconscious. He seems to be asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:09.43,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Oh, Tonio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:10.84,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,He was a good man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:15.13,Default,Azsan,0,0,0,,Lady Farnese, please order a retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:20.56,Default,Azsan,0,0,0,,Lady Farnese, was this the \Nfirst blood you've drawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:24.34,Default,Azsan,0,0,0,,As one who wields a sword,\Nyou mustn't fear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:27.68,Default,Azsan,0,0,0,,But always remember\Nthe weight of a life taken,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:30.57,Default,Azsan,0,0,0,,so long as you have men under your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:37.41,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:42.53,Default,F,0,0,0,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:43.91,Default,F,0,0,0,,All troops, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:55.84,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,Hey, are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:58.17,Default - flashback,G,0,0,0,,Yeah, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:03.46,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,Well, you're a hard one to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:09.65,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:24.57,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:29.49,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,On the battlefield, a common soldier's life \Nis worth less than a single silver coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:33.87,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,In this day and age, most people are
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:36.48,Default - flashback,,0,0,0,,abused by royalty and the nobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:41.30,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,Well, not that even kings can \Nlive as they please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:45.06,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,Everyone is merely swept along by the tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:47.51,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,The tide known as fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:48.84,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,And their lives spent,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:51.50,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,they vanish into its depths.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:54.13,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,They die before learning who they truly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:59.39,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,Some, regardless of rank or station, \Nare born as key individuals,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:00.99,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,who will shape this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:04.78,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,They are the true privileged class.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:10.25,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,I want to know who I am in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:11.91,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,What I am capable of,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:13.81,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,and what I am meant to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.17,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:20.22,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,I've never spoken to anyone about this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:22.04,Default - flashback,G,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:27.77,Default - flashback,G,0,0,0,,{\i1}the man appeared to me as something \Nbeautiful, noble, and absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:10.71,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,We have brought the Black Swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:11.38,Default,F,0,0,0,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:11.90,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Yes, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.41,Default,F,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:19.05,Default,F,0,0,0,,After you bind him to the post, \Nyou are free to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:20.28,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,But that would—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.26,Default,F,0,0,0,,No need for concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:24.45,Default,F,0,0,0,,With those gigantic shackles, \Nwhat harm could he possibly do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:26.53,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,We shall inform the vice-commander, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:27.53,Default,F,0,0,0,,That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:28.33,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:33.75,Default,F,0,0,0,,Further, instruct the guards to leave \Nthis tent until I order otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:36.00,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,But if something should happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:37.57,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,We should inform the vice-commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:39.43,Default,F,0,0,0,,What is your name and rank?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:42.46,Default,F,0,0,0,,You dare say you cannot follow my order
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,unless the vice-commander tells you to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:49.15,Default,F,0,0,0,,Tell me, who is the Supreme Commander \Nof the Holy Iron Chain Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.44,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Yes, my lady! It is you, Commander Farnese!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:54.73,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,I deeply regret speaking out of turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:56.72,Default,F,0,0,0,,As long as you bear this in mind. Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:57.19,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Yes, my lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:02.45,Default,F,0,0,0,,Black Swordsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:05.41,Default,F,0,0,0,,Or should I say... Guts, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:08.35,Default,F,0,0,0,,Before we deliver you to the Holy See,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:11.60,Default,F,0,0,0,,it falls to me, as one of the grand \Ntribunal's junior members,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:14.13,Default,F,0,0,0,,to ask you a few simple questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:17.71,Default,F,0,0,0,,Why do you laugh, cur?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:21.40,Default,G,0,0,0,,Oh, I was just thinking that \NI have the worst luck
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:23.89,Default,G,0,0,0,,with God and things of that ilk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:28.10,Default,F,0,0,0,,Blasphemy. I shan't allow you \Nto blaspheme a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:31.60,Default,F,0,0,0,,The Band of the Hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:36.02,Default,F,0,0,0,,A band of mercenaries, hired by Midland.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:37.82,Default,F,0,0,0,,The Band of the Hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:42.63,Default,F,0,0,0,,An elite military force that \Nwon countless victories,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:44.81,Default,F,0,0,0,,their military prowess\Nwas said to be peerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:48.29,Default,F,0,0,0,,But they plotted treason against the royal \Nfamily, becoming wanted fugitives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:57.64,Default,F,0,0,0,,However, the entire company \Nvanished into thin air overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:13:00.62,Default,F,0,0,0,,No one heard, even in rumors, \Nthat the bounty was claimed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:03.63,Default,F,0,0,0,,Did someone obliterate them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:06.56,Default,F,0,0,0,,All we know is that there \Nare very few survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:13.36,Default,F,0,0,0,,Th-The leader of the Band \Nof the Hawk was Griffith.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:15.30,Default,F,0,0,0,,After he went missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:18.41,Default,F,0,0,0,,it's said a woman replaced\Nhim as their leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:22.76,Default,F,0,0,0,,It's also said that the captain of their raiders
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:26.45,Default,F,0,0,0,,wielded a massive sword and could \Nslay a hundred men with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:29.24,Default,F,0,0,0,,You seem to match his description.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.04,Default,F,0,0,0,,And if I recall, his name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:32.77,Default,F,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:35.14,Default,F,0,0,0,,A questionable item,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,one that would conceivably be \Nin a heretic's possession...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:41.97,Default - flashback,Griffith,0,0,0,,Nice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:49.12,Default,F,0,0,0,,If this is a heathen idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:52.00,Default,F,0,0,0,,you will be tried as a heretic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:55.61,Default,F,0,0,0,,If you do not wish to endure that, \Nyou should confess everything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:57.33,Default,F,0,0,0,,Is that not preferable to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:14:00.21,Default,F,0,0,0,,being interrogated under torture, \Nthen burned at the stake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:02.66,Default,F,0,0,0,,Answer me, cur!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:06.49,Default,G,0,0,0,,Do you believe in God and the devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.01,Default,F,0,0,0,,What's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:09.98,Default,F,0,0,0,,Are you trying to blaspheme yet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:11.83,Default,G,0,0,0,,Have you ever met God?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:16.68,Default,F,0,0,0,,God does not show us His miraculous \Nexistence on this Earth so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:20.12,Default,F,0,0,0,,Through our faith, God is always with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:23.42,Default,F,0,0,0,,In our souls and up in Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.43,Default,F,0,0,0,,Wh-Why do you laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:29.59,Default,G,0,0,0,,What a picture-perfect response.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:31.57,Default,G,0,0,0,,Did you learn that in a convent?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:34.94,Default,G,0,0,0,,On a battlefield, a nobleman \Nsaid the exact same thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:37.97,Default,G,0,0,0,,burning a city to the ground, \Nwith its women and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:42.09,Default,G,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about some shitty, useless god
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:44.95,Default,G,0,0,0,,who's just an empty decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:48.56,Default,G,0,0,0,,A confession would be a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:50.52,Default,G,0,0,0,,I have no intention of repenting,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:53.76,Default,G,0,0,0,,and I don't think you'll learn \Nanything, even if I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:57.46,Default,G,0,0,0,,Just go say a prayer for me in \Nsome moldy temple, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:15:00.45,Default,F,0,0,0,,You cur!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.59,Default,P,0,0,0,,You just had to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:04.71,Default,F,0,0,0,,Cur,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:07.39,Default,F,0,0,0,,how dare you blaspheme in front of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander of the Holy Iron Chain Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:13.15,Default,F,0,0,0,,I was prepared to show mercy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:17.90,Default,F,0,0,0,,in consideration of your\Ninjuries, but no longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:20.04,Default,F,0,0,0,,I shall make you talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:22.29,Default,F,0,0,0,,even if it means flaying\Nthe skin from your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:24.14,Default,F,0,0,0,,I swear this by my faith!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:26.24,Default,G,0,0,0,,You're trying way too hard, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:29.03,Default,G,0,0,0,,Be it God or your rank,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever weight you're trying to \Nthrow around won't earn loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:34.72,Default,G,0,0,0,,Not like that Knight of the Bridge commands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:37.04,Default,G,0,0,0,,If you ask me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:41.73,Default,G,0,0,0,,you're just like that idol you \Nworship, all empty inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:49.01,Default,F,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.11,Default,F,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:55.56,Default,F,0,0,0,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:20.96,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Lady Farnese!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:23.79,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Excuse me... Just what is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.58,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Lady Farnese, what is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:28.13,Default,F,0,0,0,,Why all this commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:30.08,Default,F,0,0,0,,I am simply questioning him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,before we deliver him to the Holy See.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:34.37,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,However, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:35.57,Default,F,0,0,0,,I am finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:37.16,Default,F,0,0,0,,Return him to his cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.72,Default,F,0,0,0,,You are dismissed, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:40.02,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Lady Farnese...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.04,Default,F,0,0,0,,Did you not hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.41,Default,F,0,0,0,,I said, you are dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:45.44,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:46.87,Default,F,0,0,0,,Do not unshackle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:48.81,Default,F,0,0,0,,Tend his wounds, and leave him in the cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:49.93,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:50.82,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:56.71,Default,Serpico,0,0,0,,Don't be so rough on our commander, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:17:00.83,Default,Serpico,0,0,0,,She may not look it, but she \Ncan be quite charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:21.74,Default,G,0,0,0,,I can't afford to be wasting time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:22.56,Default,G,0,0,0,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:27.07,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,I don't have time to be playing \Nnice with these lunatics.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:30.52,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,Casca...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:34.47,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:37.36,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,It's nearly time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:43.08,Default,G,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.07,0:17:48.58,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,Unarmed and imprisoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.73,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,not to mention not in the best shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:51.34,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:54.09,Default,P,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:57.04,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,I guess I had this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.95,Default,P,0,0,0,,I'm here to save you, Guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:00.68,Default,P,0,0,0,,See, you can escape with this key.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:02.43,Default,G,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:05.19,Default,P,0,0,0,,Elves have a strong sense of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.19,Default,P,0,0,0,,What're you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:11.53,Default,G,0,0,0,,I'm getting my stuff back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:13.15,Default,G,0,0,0,,It's everything I have, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:19.33,Default,P,0,0,0,,But your weapons are in that woman's tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:20.84,Default,G,0,0,0,,That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:22.76,Default,G,0,0,0,,Depending how it goes, we'll take her hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:23.98,Default,P,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:28.23,Default,G,0,0,0,,I don't give a rat's ass if I end up \Nhaving to kill the lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:32.72,Default,G,0,0,0,,There's someone I need to \Nfind, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:36.42,Default,G,0,0,0,,I don't give a damn what happens \Nto those who try to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:59.55,Default,P,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:14.59,Default,F,0,0,0,,Oh, God... Please guide me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:19.10,Default,F,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:22.56,Default,P,0,0,0,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:24.42,Default,G,0,0,0,,Charming, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:32.92,Default,P,0,0,0,,You were hurt pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:35.94,Default,P,0,0,0,,You can't swing it around this soon. \NYou'll reopen the wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:39.81,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,Guess I'm still at half strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:41.23,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Lady Farnese, we have an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:42.62,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,The Black Swordsman has...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:43.60,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,You—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:45.62,Default,P,0,0,0,,That's brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:49.26,Default,G,0,0,0,,Guess I'll have to ask her along, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:19:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:00.49,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,The Black Swordsman has escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.50,Default,Knights,0,0,0,,Stop it from spreading to the other tents!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:03.97,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Lady Farnese!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.02,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:07.23,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,How did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:09.98,Default,G,0,0,0,,Step aside, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:13.28,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,You think you can escape with those injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:14.43,Default,G,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:17.87,Default,G,0,0,0,,The practice of burning people to death \Nisn't limited to clerics, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.87,0:20:18.87,Default,G,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:20.61,Default,G,0,0,0,,I'll burn her ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:24.32,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Taking a woman hostage... You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.82,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,You leave us no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:27.44,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Fall back, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:28.60,Default,G,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:35.41,Default,P,0,0,0,,What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:37.34,Default,G,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:41.84,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:43.48,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Gather the horses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:45.15,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,This is my biggest folly yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:47.31,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,We cannot let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:50.42,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:58.28,Default,P,0,0,0,,You're unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.28,0:21:02.12,Default,P,0,0,0,,Who do you think you have to\Nthank for being able to run this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:02.95,Default,G,0,0,0,,The horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:04.87,Default,P,0,0,0,,Then apologize to the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:06.20,Default,G,0,0,0,,Sorry, horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.94,Default,P,0,0,0,,As long as you remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:10.00,Default,G,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:11.52,Default,G,0,0,0,,How the tables have turned, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:13.65,Default,G,0,0,0,,Quit struggling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:16.09,Default,G,0,0,0,,With your hands tied, if you fall \Non these rocks, you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:17.18,Default,P,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.18,0:21:18.52,Default,P,0,0,0,,We won't eat you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:19.86,Default,P,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm Puck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:22.08,Default,F,0,0,0,,Let me go, cur!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:26.24,Default,F,0,0,0,,How dare you treat the Commander of the Holy Iron Chain Knights this way—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:27.22,Default,G,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:27.95,Default,P,0,0,0,,Oh, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:30.56,Default,G,0,0,0,,Keep this up, and I'll just\Nknock you out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:32.60,Default,G,0,0,0,,Sorry, you'll have to come along for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.48,Default,G,0,0,0,,And there's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:35.66,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,This is humiliating!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:37.90,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,How could a heretic do this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:39.06,Default,F,0,0,0,,Let me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:43.09,Default,F,0,0,0,,I'd rather fall and die than listen to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:45.79,Default,F,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:48.12,Default,G,0,0,0,,Just calm down a bit, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:50.97,Default,P,0,0,0,,Jeez, isn't he capable of \Nlove for his fellow man?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:51.81,Default,G,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:54.02,Default,P,0,0,0,,Sorry, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:00.92,Default,F,0,0,0,,How dare you? Don't mock me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:02.35,Default,G,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.35,0:22:03.37,Default,P,0,0,0,,She isn't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.37,0:22:03.88,Default,G,0,0,0,,Huh?
